PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX vi: <http://www.saltlux.com/transformer/views#> PREFIX kto: <http://data.visitkorea.or.kr/ontology/> PREFIX ktop: <http://data.visitkorea.or.kr/property/> PREFIX ids: <http://data.visitkorea.or.kr/resource/> PREFIX wgs: <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#> PREFIX f: <http://www.saltlux.com/geo/functions#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX geo: <http://www.saltlux.com/geo/property#> PREFIX busan: <http://lod.busan.go.kr/ontology/> PREFIX kwater: <http://opendata.kwater.or.kr/lod/def/>  SELECT ?name ?near_name ?distance  WHERE {  ids:125587 wgs:lat ?lat1 ;              wgs:long ?long1 ;            rdfs:label ?name .   (?near ?distance) geo:nearby(?lat1 ?long1 '5000') .  ?near rdfs:label ?near_name ;        ktop:category ids:A05020100 .  }

PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX vi: <http://www.saltlux.com/transformer/views#> PREFIX kto: <http://data.visitkorea.or.kr/ontology/> PREFIX ktop: <http://data.visitkorea.or.kr/property/> PREFIX ids: <http://data.visitkorea.or.kr/resource/> PREFIX wgs: <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#> PREFIX f: <http://www.saltlux.com/geo/functions#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX geo: <http://www.saltlux.com/geo/property#> PREFIX busan: <http://lod.busan.go.kr/ontology/> PREFIX kwater: <http://opendata.kwater.or.kr/lod/def/>  SELECT  ?name ?lat ?long ?address ?near ?near_name          (concat(str(?distance), 'm') AS ?dist) WHERE   { { SELECT  ?name ?lat ?long          (concat(GROUP_CONCAT(?label; SEPARATOR=' '), ' ', ?locName) AS ?address)       WHERE         { ?resource rdf:type kto:Library .           ?resource rdfs:label ?name .           ?resource wgs:lat ?lat .           ?resource wgs:long ?long .           ?resource ktop:location ?loc .           ?loc skos:broaderTransitive ?super_loc .           ?loc skos:prefLabel ?locName .           ?super_loc skos:prefLabel ?label           FILTER langMatches(lang(?label), 'KO')         }       GROUP BY ?name ?locName ?lat ?long       LIMIT   10     }     { SELECT DISTINCT  *       WHERE         { ?near rdf:type kto:Gastro .           ?near rdfs:label ?near_name .           ?near wgs:lat ?lat1 .           ?near wgs:long ?long1         }     }     BIND(f:distance(?lat, ?long, ?lat1, ?long1) AS ?distance)     FILTER ( ?distance <= 1000 )   } ORDER BY ?name ?dist LIMIT   1000

FILTER langMatches( lang(?category_name), 'KO' )  } GROUP BY ?category ?category_name

PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX vi: <http://www.saltlux.com/transformer/views#> PREFIX kto: <http://data.visitkorea.or.kr/ontology/> PREFIX ktop: <http://data.visitkorea.or.kr/property/> PREFIX ids: <http://data.visitkorea.or.kr/resource/> PREFIX wgs: <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#> PREFIX f: <http://www.saltlux.com/geo/functions#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX geo: <http://www.saltlux.com/geo/property#> PREFIX busan: <http://lod.busan.go.kr/ontology/> PREFIX kwater: <http://opendata.kwater.or.kr/lod/def/>  SELECT  ?name ?lat ?long ?address ?near ?near_name          (concat(str(?distance), 'm') AS ?dist) WHERE   { { SELECT  ?name ?lat ?long          (concat(GROUP_CONCAT(?label; SEPARATOR=' '), ' ', ?locName) AS ?address)       WHERE         { ?resource rdf:type kto:Library .           ?resource rdfs:label ?name .           ?resource wgs:lat ?lat .           ?resource wgs:long ?long .           ?resource ktop:location ?loc .           ?loc skos:broaderTransitive ?super_loc .           ?loc skos:prefLabel ?locName .           ?super_loc skos:prefLabel ?label           FILTER langMatches(lang(?label), 'KO')         }       GROUP BY ?name ?locName ?lat ?long       LIMIT   10     }     { SELECT DISTINCT  *       WHERE         { ?near rdf:type kto:Gastro .           ?near rdfs:label ?near_name .           ?near wgs:lat ?lat1 .           ?near wgs:long ?long1         }     }     BIND(f:distance(?lat, ?long, ?lat1, ?long1) AS ?distance)     FILTER ( ?distance <= 1000 )   } ORDER BY ?name ?dist LIMIT   1000

PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dc: <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX vi: <http://www.saltlux.com/transformer/views#> PREFIX kto: <http://data.visitkorea.or.kr/ontology/> PREFIX ktop: <http://data.visitkorea.or.kr/property/> PREFIX ids: <http://data.visitkorea.or.kr/resource/> PREFIX wgs: <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#> PREFIX f: <http://www.saltlux.com/geo/functions#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX geo: <http://www.saltlux.com/geo/property#> PREFIX busan: <http://lod.busan.go.kr/ontology/> PREFIX kwater: <http://opendata.kwater.or.kr/lod/def/>  SELECT (COUNT(distinct *) AS ?CNT) ?category_name WHERE {  ?resource a kto:Place ;       rdfs:label ?name ;       ktop:category ?category .   ?category skos:prefLabel ?category_name .   FILTER langMatches( lang(?category_name), 'KO' )  } GROUP BY ?category ?category_name

PREFIX  schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX  f:    <http://www.saltlux.com/geo/functions#> PREFIX  res:  <http://data.busan.go.kr/lod/resource/> PREFIX  rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX  ns:   <http://data.busan.go.kr/lod/ontology/> PREFIX  geo:  <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#> PREFIX  foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX  xsd:  <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX  rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX  skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> SELECT DISTINCT  ?uri ?label ?image ?address ?tel ?homepage WHERE   { BIND(res:부산역 AS ?res)     ?res geo:lat ?lat .     ?res geo:long ?long .     ?uri rdf:type ?class     FILTER ( ?class = ns:LodgingFacility )     ?uri rdfs:label ?label .     ?uri geo:lat ?lat2 .     ?uri geo:long ?long2     FILTER ( ?res != ?uri )     FILTER f:within_distance(?lat, ?long, ?lat2, ?long2, 5000)     BIND(f:distance(?lat, ?long, ?lat2, ?long2) AS ?distance)     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:image ?image }     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:address ?address }     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:tel ?tel }     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:homepage ?homepage }     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:content ?content }   } ORDER BY ?distance LIMIT   50

PREFIX  schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX  f:    <http://www.saltlux.com/geo/functions#> PREFIX  res:  <http://data.busan.go.kr/lod/resource/> PREFIX  rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX  ns:   <http://data.busan.go.kr/lod/ontology/> PREFIX  geo:  <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#> PREFIX  foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX  xsd:  <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX  rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX  skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> SELECT DISTINCT  ?uri ?label ?image ?address ?tel ?homepage WHERE   { BIND(res:부산역 AS ?res)     ?res geo:lat ?lat .     ?res geo:long ?long .     ?uri rdf:type ?class     FILTER ( ?class = ns:LodgingFacility )     ?uri rdfs:label ?label .     ?uri geo:lat ?lat2 .     ?uri geo:long ?long2     FILTER ( ?res != ?uri )     FILTER f:within_distance(?lat, ?long, ?lat2, ?long2, 5000)     BIND(f:distance(?lat, ?long, ?lat2, ?long2) AS ?distance)     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:image ?image }     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:address ?address }     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:tel ?tel }     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:homepage ?homepage }     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:content ?content }   } ORDER BY ?distance LIMIT   50

FILTER ( ?movieUri != ?res )     }

PREFIX  schema: <http://schema.org/> PREFIX  f:    <http://www.saltlux.com/geo/functions#> PREFIX  res:  <http://data.busan.go.kr/lod/resource/> PREFIX  rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX  ns:   <http://data.busan.go.kr/lod/ontology/> PREFIX  geo:  <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#> PREFIX  foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX  xsd:  <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX  rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX  skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> SELECT DISTINCT  ?uri ?label ?image ?address ?tel ?homepage WHERE   { BIND(res:부산역 AS ?res)     ?res geo:lat ?lat .     ?res geo:long ?long .     ?uri rdf:type ?class     FILTER ( ?class = ns:LodgingFacility )     ?uri rdfs:label ?label .     ?uri geo:lat ?lat2 .     ?uri geo:long ?long2     FILTER ( ?res != ?uri )     FILTER f:within_distance(?lat, ?long, ?lat2, ?long2, 5000)     BIND(f:distance(?lat, ?long, ?lat2, ?long2) AS ?distance)     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:image ?image }     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:address ?address }     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:tel ?tel }     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:homepage ?homepage }     OPTIONAL       { ?uri ns:content ?content }   } ORDER BY ?distance LIMIT   50

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>  PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>  PREFIX knpsc: <http://lod.knps.or.kr/schema/class/> PREFIX knpsp: <http://lod.knps.or.kr/schema/property/> PREFIX wgs84: <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> SELECT DISTINCT ?RoadKill ?label ?nationalpark ?nationalparkName ?lat ?long ?parkoffice ?parkofficeName ?date ?numberofIndividual ?remark ?section {   	?RoadKill  a knpsc:RoadKill. 	optional {?RoadKill rdfs:label ?label. FILTER(lang(?label) = 'ko')} 	?RoadKill  knpsp:nationalpark ?nationalpark.    	filter(regex(str(?nationalpark), 'knps')) . 	optional {?nationalpark foaf:name ?nationalparkName.  FILTER(lang(?nationalparkName) = 'ko')} 	filter(regex(str(?nationalparkName), '계룡산')) . 	?RoadKill  wgs84:lat ?lat. 	?RoadKill  wgs84:long ?long. 	?RoadKill  knpsp:parkoffice ?parkoffice. 	optional {?parkoffice rdfs:label ?parkofficeName.
